Package: rdeps
Title: Automatically Obtain Source Code for all Dependencies of a given R Package
Version: 0.0.0
Authors@R: person("Mark", "Padgham", email = "mark.padgham@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Automatically obtain source code for all dependencies of a given R
    package, either by opening github sites in browser, or downloading .tar.gz
    files.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    XML
Suggests:
    knitr,
    roxygen2,
    rmarkdown,
    devtools,
    testthat
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/mpadge/rdeps
BugReports: https://github.com/mpadge/rdeps/issues
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
